    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 that defines mechanical excellence. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting a 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous transitional throttle response. The double VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure precise variable valve timing, while the rod bearings have been addressed as preventative maintenance. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension setup that retains factory-spec kinematics. The exterior finish exhibits full depth and clarity, free of any road-rash or imperfections. This is a turnkey, concours-level machine for the discerning driver.",
