    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just left the showroom floor. This car has been exclusively stored in a climate-controlled environment and has never been exposed to inclement weather. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless, featuring original paint with a mirror-like depth and zero imperfections, rock chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains taut and supple without a single crease, and the original carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, backed by a complete, chronological service history from certified technicians. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive example of the model.",
